features: Lamp with Dual Illumination: Our desk lamp features a cool dual-head design, stretching 180° both ways for awesome lighting flexibility. The dual-head design splits into two beams of light, concentrating for enhanced brightness or dispersing to cover a larger illuminated area. This makes our desk lamp an ideal choice for sewing tables, card tables, reading, study, and crafting! 🌈💡

5 Lighting Modes & 10 Brightness Levels: Our desk light rocks 5 color modes (3000K-6000K), each with 10 brightness levels, catering to everything from reading to crafting. It packs a built-in reading mode, fixed at a cozy 4000K warm light. Effortlessly switch to reading mode—no time wasted adjusting settings. Dive into your reading time pronto! 📚💡

Timer & Memory Function: Desktop lamp rocks a 45-min auto-shutdown timer, so no worries about forgetting to turn it off after late-night reading or work. This feature not only safeguards your sleep but also saves energy. The table lamp supports startup memory, remembering your last lighting mode for a personalized setup. Easy peasy! 🌙💡

Touch Control & USB Charging Phones: This modern lamp features touch control—just a gentle touch and you're in control. Plus, it packs a built-in USB port. When the LED lamp's on, you can charge your phone at the same time, keeping your desktop as tidy as can be. Super convenient! 💡🔌

Versatile Desk Light: The small lamp rocks a bold and stylish appearance, instantly elevating the room's vibe. Crafted from aluminum alloy and plastic, it strikes a perfect balance of quality and lightweight, making it easy to carry. The wide base, equipped with soft anti-slip pads, ensures stable support. Ideal for home office, makeup, manicures/pedicures, art and crafts, reading/studying, and travel. 💡🌟

manufacturerProductDescription.media_text: Woputne Desk Lamp Good for reading, home working, study, craft, nail art at home, video call, etc

Double-Head with Flexible Design Led Dual Head Desk Lamp with Pencil Holder 5 Lighting Colors with 10 Dimmable Brightnesswith Plastic Pen Container: keep Desk Clean:Dual USB Charging Port: 5V 2A Input Port; 5V 1A Output Port.Mains plug is not included ️Tip: Manual ON/OFF Switch behind the desk lamp, controls the power; When the button is Off, the desk light will not light up

Space-saving & Portable The swivel arm of the double lights can be extended horizontally by 180° or folded vertically by 180°, and the base can be rotated 130°. The foldable design makes it easy to carry and place desk lamps for home offices.

Touch Control The light's touch control panel is intuitive to operate and allows for easy adjustment of brightness and color settings. Brush Pot Pens, rulers, and tools fit in the built-in pen holder. Makes it easier to store your items.

Built-in USB Charging Includes USB charging port (5V 1A), which means you can charge all your other USB devices, such as cell phones, smart watches, tablets, etc., while working with the desk lamp. Reading Lamp You can easily switch desk reading lamp to reading mode and start enjoying your reading time without wasting time adjusting the lighting mode.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on January 28, 2024
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Great lighting with multiple options
reviews.reviewText: Biggest surprise was this lamp is really light. It has multiple shades of light with various configurations to use the light arms. Easy set up. I use it for watercolor and it works great.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on February 7, 2024
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Light it up!
reviews.reviewText: I love love love my light, it gives me just the amount of light on my desk. I have a couple of plants on my desk and although it's not a grow light it seems to help the plants. I love the thin stature and the availability to position each arm, and to boot the lighting levels and colors are fantastic.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on January 18, 2024
reviews.reviewTitle: 3.0 out of 5 stars Cheap Option to brightening up your desk
reviews.reviewText: Thinking it has 2 extended arms will cover wider range of light. Unfortunately, the height is not adjustable. When I put it next to monitor, the arms will fight for space with the monitors.The ON/OFF button is very sensitive and there is no hepatic impact upon touching it. I could easily put my finger in the wrong area, which eventually adjusted the brightness or "reading-mode" on the unit.Lastly, it does not come with the AC adaptor. The unit only comes with the regular USB-A to USB-C cable. It is not very long, so you may need to replace the cable or have a USB-A hub on your desk to plug it.Bottom line is if you are looking for quick and affordable light for your desk, this unit is working as it should. There is nothing fancy since it is made of plastics and the arm height / length are not adjustable.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on November 20, 2023
reviews.reviewTitle: 4.0 out of 5 stars Good lamp, didn't realize it was a USB plug
reviews.reviewText: Nice desk lamp. Gives good light in a range of warmth and brightness. I didn't realize when I ordered it that it was a USB plug, but I guess that's the world we live in now.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on October 11, 2023
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Adequate desk lamp
reviews.reviewText: It is not top-of-the-line, but provides enough light and is a good height to provide light over the top of my laptop screen. It is 360 degree flexible for uplighting or any direction. Includes USB powered port in back I am using to charge my phone and a USB to USB-C cable for power- no power block provided, however. Pencil cup is dumb. Wireless charger in same place would have been cool. 38 LEDs- 19 on each side. Light color selection is nice feature- ranges from warm white to cool white. Includes 45-minute sleep timer and a "reading" selection that changes the color to something like "night light" for Windows. Draws a bit of power with phone charging, so use a 2 amp power block or larger if not powering from your computer's USB.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on December 6, 2023
reviews.reviewTitle: 1.0 out of 5 stars Not really that bright and chord sucks
reviews.reviewText: Figured it would be a lot brighter than it is and they give you a type c to usb chord that’s only about 2.5’ long and no power block. Using this on a desk I figured they would give you a longer chord and a plug to actually use the light. If the return place for Amazon wasn’t 30 minutes away I would return this. Definitely false advertising.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on January 6, 2024
reviews.reviewText: Perfect for my home office love the ability to change settings of lights and the color! Very satisfied! Love the pun holder that’s just a bonus!!!!
